      <p class="- topic/p ">The<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Business Unit</uicontrol>formenables you to categorize projectsand users based on the organization's operational functions. Users assigned to a particular business unit can access only projects that are associated with that business unit. You can assign multiple business units to a user and only one business unit to a project.</p>
